{"tid":1032613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑店回帶］大家經過灣仔188對面嗰陣要小心","createTime":"2019-02-22T13:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T14:44:53.000Z","uid":144024,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a477a4147316faef2ddccf162f7f52c20e8ebb1","tid":1032613,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱放工無嘢做，就去行188。<br />\n行完諗住過對面街去食腸粉王，咁我嗰陣一路行一路篤電話回message嘅。<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦有條友遞張卡片比我（我以為係派傳單嗰啲），禮貌上咪接囉，點知隻手就掂到張卡片嗰陣，條友忽然縮翻手，再搶走咗我副眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶眼鏡嘅人應該知，比人搞鳩自己副眼鏡會好火架嘛，我咪左手扯實佢件衫，再fing佢落地。嗰下因為唔知乜事，即刻右手捉實手提，再將背包轉返去前面再攬實（以為大陸嗰啲前面搵人搞你，後面有人𠝹袋）。<br />\n<br />\n隻左手一直死捉住條友件衫唔放。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢做乜撚嘢，條友話見我副眼鏡好污糟，又鬆鬆地，話諗住幫我拎入鋪洗兼較返好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我梗係話唔使，叫佢比返副眼鏡我。條友又話好快就得，又話我壓住佢好痛叫我比佢起身先（嗰陣我用左膝壓住佢個肚唔比佢走）。我就企硬佢唔比返我就報警。<br />\n<br />\n之後條友就比返副眼鏡我，話誤會。<br />\n之後有途人映相，又有人話間鋪好有名，成人搶人眼鏡屈人入去買嘢，叫我咪信條友呀。<br />\n<br />\n我嗰下真心唔知乜事，拎返眼鏡就走咗。<br />\n<br />\n之後google 下就發現原來間嘢好有名，由葵浦呃到去灣仔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110306/15043739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110306%2F15043739&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=daba192f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20110306%2F15043739&h=6ff263c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20110306/15043739</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/03/12/YO1703120014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2017%2F03%2F12%2FYO1703120014.htm&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=e5384ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/03/12/YO1703120014.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n連登都有人講過<br />\n<br />\n灣仔黑店名門眼鏡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/166928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/166928</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解呃咗咁多年都仲喺度仲未收皮。<br />\n大家經過真係要小心。"},{"pid":"272f8da9b13238cfe18eb3427bdab0f11b7a66fa","tid":1032613,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"補充多少少<br />\n<br />\n間嘢叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名門眼鏡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咪撚比佢呃到"},{"pid":"845da9b97e56be06fa91922123dd941d4cb96cf6","tid":1032613,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a4f70106b58259b66569b426e189e1f2260fa8","tid":1032613,"uid":39496,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"打能到佢仆街就啱"},{"pid":"8a39454c684dcbd493a5a1434e13aac1f16b7305","tid":1032613,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2a4f70106b58259b66569b426e189e1f2260fa8","tid":1032613,"uid":39496,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"打能到佢仆街就啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:40:21.000Z","msg":"我嗰下完全唔知乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心以為後面有人𠝹袋偷嘢。<br />\n<br />\n點會有人無啦啦搶眼鏡架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a4e43661f572fa9aed9350be78a3e159150e23","tid":1032613,"uid":49978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"係咪葵廣果間"},{"pid":"4c52484e92bb01dda6e582a925985c60542d6154"